title: Union's Bar
user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Constantin Hauss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXy8dmd-7cIVBWqmSK9tonjEe10y45p_ny5yTr03KTVHM0a2sGw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Union Euper Bar: Ein Verstecktes Highlight in Abtsdorf

Die Union Euper Bar in Abtsdorf ist ein wahrer Geheimtipp für alle, die eine erstklassige Bar mit lokalem Charme suchen. Schon beim Betreten wird man von der herzlichen Atmosphäre und dem rustikalen, doch stilvollen Interieur begrüßt. Die Mischung aus traditioneller und moderner Dekoration schafft eine einzigartige, einladende Stimmung.

Die Getränkekarte der Union Euper Bar beeindruckt durch Vielfalt und Qualität. Neben einer umfangreichen Auswahl an klassischen Mischgetränken und regionalen Bieren bietet die Bar auch eine interessante Auswahl an exklusiven Eigenkreationen. Die "Kroko-Runde" ist besonders zu empfehlen.

Der Service in der Union Euper Bar ist bemerkenswert. Das Personal ist nicht nur freundlich und aufmerksam, sondern auch äußerst kompetent. Sie nehmen sich die Zeit, individuelle Vorlieben zu erfragen und passende Empfehlungen zu geben, was den Besuch zu einem persönlichen Erlebnis macht.

Ein weiterer Pluspunkt ist die Musik, die die Atmosphäre perfekt abrundet. Eine ausgewogene Mischung aus aktuellen Hits und zeitlosen Klassikern sorgt für die richtige Stimmung und lädt zum Verweilen ein.

Zusammengefasst ist die Union Euper Bar in Abtsdorf ein Ort, der durch seine gemütliche Atmosphäre, die hervorragenden Getränke und den exzellenten Service besticht. Für Einheimische und Besucher gleichermaßen ist diese Bar ein Muss und bietet die perfekte Kulisse für einen unvergesslichen Abend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3F9FeTn1HPg5sJ_-38g5mjM1KnZcxE58IvyCE&fid=0x0:0x6172156ff5a667c7"],"When":"2024-6-6"},{"Name":"Hubi Koppe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1wHCDoyyUCDGUS_eCbBv7wwS7x0Qrg4WDsxRIeuxZKx0n_QMp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Das verlockende Angebot verschiedenster Kaltgetränke, konnte mich nun schon einige Male in dieses Familienbetriebene Lokal führen.
Es ist immer wieder einen Besuch wert!

Danke an die Betreiber!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leon Nagel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnLhmUjnvInV0hZw0BZSXF2kx7Gar11WcpIWucG3ObSGjJ5A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Eine sehr idyllische Bar zum Kaltgetränke trinken.🍻
Danke für dieses Konzept.

MfG Leon de Nagel","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"The Grimreaper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlTmVUsoSV_UT5gE5DXCHqp3B3wbjb_XDwWVN6454pq3yPxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Immer ein Heidenspaß, beste Bar die ich kenne","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julia & Carlos K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGsdXxOaOI7aGEzXSxrbCAjBbx9BXDvWs2pXdmypIY3YiLgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Es werden wunderbare Kaltgetränke serviert.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Martin Zimmer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFLyg7uJTNOWbn23SkSDJn8LVNPl3tq8dylBZvr9gNuA1lWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ein sehr gemütlicher Ort mit nicht zu heißen Würstchen","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frank Grüneberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJaCMabd9_5TX5DPAcGl2iNEMCfiYMeqHOnaWbC6sAxHJtG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leon Nagel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtC8sFmzh-Og1LQeuMtfnHtZXxvuQEQHXOLV2ZZxGET1BeQc4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"","Images":null,"When":""}]

title: Wallwitzhof
user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Dina Lewicki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbAcGxa1ljpyaCV8wsHg-Vc0nas_PNMzTyDGZxcey-bSOcC70U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wunderbare Gästewohnung mit vielen Antiquitäten liebevoll eingerichtet und dekoriert. Super freundliche, herzliche Gastgeber, die uns auch gute Tipps für Restaurants und Sehenswürdigkeiten in Wittenberg gegeben haben. Alles ist vom Wallwitzhof aus zu Fuß erreichbar.
Die Gästewohnung ist sehr geräumig mit mehreren Zimmern und echt jedes ist mit anderen Möbeln ausgestattet. Alles ist sehr sauber.
Auch mit Motorrädern ist es kein Problem - wir bekamen einen überdachten Parkplatz im Innenhof.
Wir waren wunschlos glücklich und unsere Erwartungen wurden übertroffen. Kommen definitiv wieder mal nach Wittenberg und wollen wieder hier übernachten.
Danke für alles und liebe Grüße 🖖","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNG8C1LTM1x66nKgmdvFn7lC1JTY7x9uge9NoaH&fid=0x0:0x48f83e2b5454c90c"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Angelina Hoenning","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJcsVibvPMcS5Pj8Ho8PchcuVUtF2H3QgRCyeRpGE-4yLQbpg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sehr herzlich, toller kleiner Weihnachtsmarkt, Glühwein schmeckt, schönes Ambiente und ein sehr netter Chef :) kommen gerne wieder!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Markus P.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_DLHZ6uaqKNBtayUmTrK5kUA6A0ycnhhA4-iYrFOsmR6B66c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Der beste Hof zur Weihnachtsmarktzeit. Gemütliches Ambiente, sehr netter Service, der Glühwein schmeckt. Glatte Empfehlung.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Silke W.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFsb2Gcr2LEg2T5ZUkncMxRTG3ILVt3g6JUkCunh0wlyf2sw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sehr schöne große Ferienwohnung,  liebevoll antik dekoriert und gestaltet. Es gibt soviel zu schauen, dass man meint in einem kleinen Museum zu sein. Es wirkt alles sehr stilvoll zusammen gestellt.  Die Gastgeber sehr nett, freundlich und aufmerksam. Die Wohnung liegt im Zentrum der Lutherstadt Wittenberg, ideal um sich auf Luthers Spuren zu begeben. Für größere Entfernungen stehen zwei super Fahrräder zur Verfügung,  die wir gerne genutzt haben. Wir kommen gerne wieder!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNu_9GRq_fpZN7B3-62sXm9A38--9oD2SkMCBsp&fid=0x0:0x48f83e2b5454c90c"],"When":"2022-4-26"},{"Name":"Ulrike S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdAoI53Nctj0Xh8p4rD2_Bt840AcP71dihYiCkVajA02OEnflc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sehr schöner Hof, mit entspannter Atmosphäre, leckeren Glühwein und sehr netten Besitzern.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgk3ooVAQsgPCzskkXstwzakl-brEahez8GGQ8&fid=0x0:0x48f83e2b5454c90c"],"When":"2022-12-11"},{"Name":"Thomas Kirschner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILCYVwBLgC4bJCnTidpRxs891VJ0NeCSUW-luRtuBEAtGNQA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tolle zentrale Lage, historisch restauriert, liebevoll eingerichtet und ein sehr freundlicher Empfang","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1GaocEzaASm_Q-qbPBAPnjnat6XKAM1k_rnDf&fid=0x0:0x48f83e2b5454c90c"],"When":"2022-1-23"},{"Name":"Martina Kunze","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7aOT3cRKL697pecUTGWTO1BKD2xQp11750Q30yHJWMFqWeVkkgQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wunderschöner kleiner romantischer Weihnachtsmarkt","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shamanne X","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEoFDKgclnE1KlmdNphPQWqSA1hwPIPBR94_8ONuoxb8t_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nur lecker Caipi getrunken. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Angelica Meydam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVI-mcKkeAvSvQHwx6yZp9K1YWRFqOBkFdQpQQLmGO1IZXuv93t=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very competitive pricing, worth the drive! Everything we ate was top notch 👌🏽
Fry Bread & Beer Cheese 🤤🤤🤤
Beer Battered Walleye could not have been better. And the Miss Piggy Burger with pork and cheese, tasted like quality barbecued ribs on a burger that was very good!
Walking in at 5:30 for fish fry on a Friday night was an hour wait but it was worth it. The atmosphere is really nice. Cozy yet trendy remodel with high ceilings and lots of windows in the dining area at the back of the building.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOrL8i_w2suUUPrEKW7psgGn6hSakjhRfDvRvl8&fid=0x0:0x5ccde4784b50a38d"],"When":"2025-1-25"},{"Name":"Monica Abraham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4BZp063N8s6ziRJrsOgoMFUG7OZnGvjSAAg7dC2DFEOFBpfu7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This bar/restaurant is incredible. The atmosphere is great and every member of the staff was so friendly! The food was incredible too. I have never been to a bar that had lobster in so many dishes. I got the street corn nachos and added lobster and it was the best meal I have ever eaten! My husband had the lobster croissant and it was a heaping pile of lobster on a delicious croissant. We will drive the 40 minutes from home just to eat here again!!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNw9OG47vBRKd7jAmOt2ho99KggHjFwrC958Oyq&fid=0x0:0x5ccde4784b50a38d"],"When":"2023-4-22"},{"Name":"Katie Lemke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJjEvdjdCV4JpjaT7gYzYBPsXnZRJBYxZXauDosVgLDaKHoxRJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food! Love the variety. The deep fried balls with cheese are legit the best. The menu prices are competitive and honestly it cost us more to eat at fast food so we elect for good food! But love the remodel and it looks small from the outside but once you walk in you’ll be pleasantly surprised by the amount of room and kid friendly they are! Don’t be afraid to make this your next dinner spot. Definitely worth the effort.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP57L2kJMAPzfCmVv45KhQPifZT5f7uCWKy7D3d&fid=0x0:0x5ccde4784b50a38d"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"Sheanon Riley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_97JTOJiu3WLeoW-VCLglKRfGLOt1EMNAtAK0AzzNcli0IQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolute treasure. Right off Rte. 29, walking distance from Wilderness Crossing Travel Center. Staff is welcoming and friendly and the place as a whole is clearly a labor of love. Inside and outside, it's like being at your best friends home. An eclectic mixup, best attributes of a dive bar and an upscale gastropub. I missed the kitchen closing time, but the bar itself did not disappoint. Beer selection was great, liquor selection was exceptional. Places like this are few and far between, understandable because Rachel's outshines them all! Again, can't say enough about the staff. Ashley and Caitlin (so sorry of I spelled it wrong!) are phenomenal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOai2ekGGnDJgCUsIgRsi6G9Ts9I9zUlJWuxEhb&fid=0x0:0x5ccde4784b50a38d"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Daniel Karwowski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQ3FC0t76mmXrMIg7a5X4h17LSDWpJMxuPZr21kTY7IbKJOJg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really like this stop on the road up north. It's the first time I've ever seen a pool table outside! I was treated well by the staff very friendly! It's worth a look there's an outside beer garden type thing where you could sit outside and order. I seen a lot of motorcyclists there so it's popular with the
two wheelers

I did not eat there because I was in between meals arrived at the wrong time to eat. So I can't speak about the food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Craig & Bernice","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVb1Q_ZD_HW5ZxjHgCawlUhnYflL15aLgyhdFkdK4HG0TRNQ6bD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We absolutely love this pace and the bartenders are top notch.. On our way back down from north woods we love to stop
For lunch.. Menu is great a variety for everyone!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOB9M1zH3gnFAmVb6HvYJaW4FvtyFktu9U6I_c&fid=0x0:0x5ccde4784b50a38d"],"When":"2024-4-21"},{"Name":"Kimberly C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7TwCMJY7LyBcRgnh2ESpp6pS2mnuNe_RG5b2sRMXiq6uDFPUl=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a cool place. Saw the sign on 29 and decided to check it out. There is a patio and I saw patrons with their pups! Service was excellent; server explained immediately that there would be a delay with food orders, but the appetizers came out fairly quickly and the drinks were almost immediate.

Get the cheese curds!

Food is good and the menu is creative, you've got pub staples like burgers, and then you have fun stuff, like lobster tacos! Yum. Oh and a Thai curry soup  was divine.

There's tabletop and others games as well as ongoing trivia on television screens. Even the bathroom is cool.

Great place to hang out with good food and a cool atmosphere. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kate Chartrand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIV2miBjLhIXiDyRSK0Cnxcqpf-BvdtiALWqacSC4-puO9z3w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent lunch while traveling through! Very clean bar & grill, friendly staff, outdoor seating available. I had the Cuban croissant sandwich & my husband had the bacon bourbon burger with beer fries, both meals really tasty!","Images":null,"When":""}]

Burger was ok   Atmosphere was meh.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Letitia Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXg4xkEXLtDZ_acPNBvxZd2CnZqPcuTX7Fb74uFnzlm_arovxwVmg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Walleye fish taste like perfection! The garlic parmesan chippers and shrimp tacos were delicious as well! And, the price for what I received and the portion was affordable. I'd come back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cherie Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4eE4U2cPnqvmU3Y9dBxQ6q34R71tUajJV9v7chwiZ_NIb1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My son \u0026 I went for the fish fry, and I'm super glad we did. We sat at the bar, although there is a room off the bar area with tables if that's your preference. It was our first time here and we were greeted warmly by the staff behind the bar. FANTASTIC hand-muddled Old Fashion. Seriously, the best I've had maybe ever! Our food came quickly and was DELICIOUS with good sized portions. Both of us ordered the haddock, me with broasted wedges and the kidlet had French fries. The dinners also come with toasted rye bread and coleslaw. You definitely get a lot of value here for your money. The staff was friendly \u0026 attentive. One of the best dining-out experiences I've had in quite a while. Will absolutely be back!","Images":null,"When":""}]

If you are in Wittenberg, make sure you enjoy a drink here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leon Wania","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrMz4TK94xIPVGcSSpttEmPLq83gON3df9qeO8w1zsq5YqG95flw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious, well made and nicely priced cocktails.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rainer Wolf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyQMROLyOLVxuLX4065i0I5NJ-O_1AtXJSx0RLnSDVrkCf3FzC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Signature cocktails with excellent service at reasonable prices.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"KLaus-Peter Ott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJc9fPa4plzThPq7hWKSxJA3l1FGGcd27m9IA7T_BQZs-GJPA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Top","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Manuela","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGf3TeEkeMwzBQ-9SLTXtUrke1QQbFieJ3zAetwivAhjMoJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ich war absolut begeistert. Wir hatten verschiedene Cocktails und jeder war ein einzigartiges Erlebnis. So besondere Kreationen und auch die Art, wie jeder individuell ganz verschieden angerichtet war..ich kenne nichts vergleichbares! Wer gern auch mal neue und ungewöhnliche und doch völlig stimmige Variationen probiert, sollte hier unbedingt einkehren. Das Personal war übrigens auch sehr angenehm und kompetent, die Räumlichkeiten authentisch und gepflegt, ein rundum tolles Konzept. Vielen Dank!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTcIz84KE11HsdKjnjy7Z5ZUYKlTBXW1A-Uh6j\u0026fid=0x0:0x7fe8ccb2e5aa4fe7"],"When":"2024-7-17"},{"Name":"Horst Feratu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_Dyv6lEvcUhvktySteBgg5hp0BiC99ZRFVtx_tnLA9T4cJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Edit: bei der pampigen Antwort mußte ich sogar noch mal nach unten korrigieren. Was sie in ihrer Arbeitszeit aufwischen oder putzen ist mir ziemlich egal. Ich finde solche Details eher abstoßend und ihrer Unternehmung, die ja Genuss kreieren soll, abträglich, abr gut, das müssen sie ja wissen.\nDer Service kam leider nicht so ganz hinterher. Der Chef macht auch eher nur sporadisch mit, man hat ja zwei Titel mal geholt. Der erste Drink war noch ganz gut, aber der zweite (Sakura Martini) war einfach nur harter Sprit der nach penetrantem Parfum riecht und lieblos serviert wurde. Es gibt hier schöne Sachen zu trinken, aber mit dem Teil hat man sich keinen Gefallen getan. Das gibt es in Berlin an jeder Ecke besser (leider).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOc-l2139VtGRS4INlNJMk1NgWEbFzHqv7Qy_fp\u0026fid=0x0:0x7fe8ccb2e5aa4fe7"],"When":"2024-8-9"}]

Kinda small on the inside, but a lot of tables outside. Casual food such as burgers and fries, but they definitely made it their own. Everything was just a little more gourmet. Would definitely go back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSzWOSfGstjpvj4Jwyve2Wr7rz7NbuHeNfijam\u0026fid=0x0:0xcb3264f4f8f33884"],"When":"2018-3-29"},{"Name":"Shaleena Quinlan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXh-ga6veDfWZLelRRTCaGQ3zS1NBGH2GJeZDbewe2LrouakiJhxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I thoroughly enjoyed the chicken burger I had here and would gladly get it again. Do stop here if you get the chance.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7Sp_3050rIXDkAiJnJfuux60LR5_P51mjCNed\u0026fid=0x0:0xcb3264f4f8f33884"],"When":"2018-3-23"},{"Name":"Ann Joy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMBjzMFi8VL5Tmt-Up1AF3IEFgMrCaCAPktjbn4paaBCmXa8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was very very tasty and lots of options for vegeterians!\nAlthough fries were too dry.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOanRnfrA_iN7KhNfxi1GLMxAacdkfYlfxHs0ZB\u0026fid=0x0:0xcb3264f4f8f33884"],"When":"2022-8-1"}]

Das geht besser!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Uwe shorty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVU83sAVwO7Po4Y-oq13lLmEdzs7XIECzxzYBbMT1rSXTD9oLLe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"die Cocktails haben ihren Namen nicht verdient, der Mai Tai hatte nichts mit dem selbigen zu tun, blanker Alkohol…","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"StuFFii Xx","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAIb1ocVcLFjGGoQHe1D132bTEdhzcnsTCihDcpC79UjAS4Sx5Og=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super entspannte Atmosphäre\nFreundliche Bedienung\nImmer wieder schön hier einen Abend zu verbringen.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-VSaDSqUqzgzuWyMQfeY_TN01v7R8Jd5FUM8r\u0026fid=0x0:0xf9ce8c4c62d64b3c"],"When":"2022-11-26"},{"Name":"Manuel Pinnecke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9dTissLL3iTA0V7AusYT_dp5YMJb2rV5XujY3qjcl4n-WGH8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Die Coco Bar präsentiert eine Band, die mit rechten und rechtsextremen Ansichten in Verbindung steht. Zum Beispiel nutzt die Krähe-Band die Bühne, um ihre falschen Überzeugungen zu verbreiten, und der Sänger Stefan Krähe zieht fragwürdige Vergleiche mit Juden. Es stellt sich die Frage, ob diese Unternehmen nicht genauer darüber nachdenken, welche Bands sie in ihre Bar holen. Ich kann die Coco Bar daher nicht empfehlen. Es wäre ratsam, vor der Auswahl von Bands sorgfältig darüber nachzudenken, welche Botschaften und Werte sie repräsentieren, um negative Konnotationen zu vermeiden.","Images":null,"When":""}]
